          "id": "cue-c00762c2babe",
          "atMs": 250,
          "text": "Game Builder saves layers, tile art, actors, transforms, and typed properties in a plain game file. The generated companion class binds names such as player, enemy, and flag to Java fields, while explicit arcade behavior enables gravity, running, jumping, patrols, pickups, collision, and camera follow.",
